name: Matlab-image-sp14
body:
### Image Processing with MATLAB
How can MATLAB be used to process image data from an external source?  We will discuss the Image Processing Toolbox and topics like particle-velocity tracking (PVT) and automatic feature identification.

This page will be updated as we draw closer to the event.

[CSE Training](http://cse.illinois.edu/training)
